    public class DataSourceImpl
extends NodeImpl
implements DataSource
    An implementation of the model object 'Data Source'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Data Source Service
    • Library Configurations
    • Url
    • Queries
    • Dependencies Library
    • Target Library
    • Fetch Variable Query
